[
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">How</st> <st data-num=\"04970\" class=\"\">long</st> do <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> intend to <st data-num=\"056\" class=\"\">mourn</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st>? <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> have <st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">rejected</st> him as <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"04390\" class=\"\">Fill</st> your <st data-num=\"07161\" class=\"\">horn</st> with <st data-num=\"08081\" class=\"\">olive oil</st> and <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">go</st>. I am <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sending</st> you <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st> in <st data-num=\"01022\" class=\"\">Bethlehem</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> I have <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">selected</st> a <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> for myself from among his <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0349\" class=\"\">How</st> can I <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">go</st>? <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> will <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hear</st> about it and <st data-num=\"02026\" class=\"\">kill</st> me!\u201d But the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">Take</st> a <st data-num=\"05697 01241\">heifer</st> with <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">you</st><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, \u2018I have <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> to <st data-num=\"02076\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span>.\u2019",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "Then <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">invite</st> <st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st> to the <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st>, and <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">show</st> you <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">what</st> you should <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">do</st>. You will <st data-num=\"04886\" class=\"\">anoint</st> for me <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">the one</st> I <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">point out</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> you.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">did</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">told</st> him.<n id=\"1\" /> When he <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">arrived</st> in <st data-num=\"01035\" class=\"\">Bethlehem</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"02205\" class=\"\">elders</st> of the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> <st data-num=\"02729\" class=\"\">were afraid</st> to <st data-num=\"07122\" class=\"\">meet</st> him. They<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cDo you <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> in <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">peace</st>?\u201d ",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cYes, in <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">peace</st>. I have <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> to <st data-num=\"02076\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">Consecrate</st> yourselves and <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> me to the <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st>.\u201d So he <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">consecrated</st> <st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st> and his <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> and <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">invited</st> them to the <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">When</st> they <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">arrived</st>, Samuel<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">noticed</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0446\" class=\"\">Eliab</st> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to himself,<n id=\"3\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"0389\" class=\"\">Surely</st>, here <st data-num=\"05048\" class=\"\">before</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> stands his <st data-num=\"04899\" class=\"\">chosen king</st>.\u201d<n id=\"4\" /> ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "But the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">Don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"05027\" class=\"\">be impressed</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">by</st><n id=\"1\" /> his <st data-num=\"04758\" class=\"\">appearance</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">or</st> his <st data-num=\"01364 06967\">height</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> I have <st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">rejected</st> him. <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> does <st data-num=\"03588 03808\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">view</st> things <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">the way</st> <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">do</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03588 0120\">People</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">look</st> on the <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">outward appearance</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> but the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">looks</st> at the <st data-num=\"03824\" class=\"\">heart</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st> <st data-num=\"07121 0413\">called</st> <st data-num=\"041\" class=\"\">Abinadab</st> and <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">presented</st> him <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> But Samuel<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cThe <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">chosen</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this one</st> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">either</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "Then <st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">presented</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"08048\" class=\"\">Shammah</st>. But Samuel <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cThe <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">chosen</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this one</st> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">either</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">presented</st> <st data-num=\"07651\" class=\"\">seven</st> of his <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> But <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st>, \u201cThe <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">chosen</st> any of <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "Then <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559 0413\" class=\"\">asked</st> <st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"08552\" class=\"\">Is</st> that <st data-num=\"08552\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">young men</st>?\u201d Jesse<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cThere <st data-num=\"07604\" class=\"\">is</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">still</st> the <st data-num=\"06996\" class=\"\">youngest one</st>, <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">but</st> he\u2019s <st data-num=\"07462\" class=\"\">taking care</st> of the <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">flock</st>.\u201d <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">Send</st> and <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">get</st> him, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> we <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">cannot</st> <st data-num=\"05437\" class=\"\">turn</st> our attention to other things <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">until</st> he <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">comes</st> <st data-num=\"06311\" class=\"\">here</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So Jesse <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">had</st> him <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">brought in</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> Now <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> was <st data-num=\"0132\" class=\"\">ruddy</st>, <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> <st data-num=\"03303\" class=\"\">attractive</st> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st> and a <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">handsome</st> <st data-num=\"07210\" class=\"\">appearance</st>. The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">Go</st> and <st data-num=\"04886\" class=\"\">anoint</st> him. <st data-num=\"03588 02088\">This</st> is the <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">one</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">took</st> the <st data-num=\"07161\" class=\"\">horn</st> full of <st data-num=\"08081\" class=\"\">olive oil</st> and <st data-num=\"04886\" class=\"\">anointed</st> him in the <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">presence</st> of his <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">brothers</st>. The <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">Spirit</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"06743\" class=\"\">rushed</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">upon</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> from <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> <st data-num=\"04605\" class=\"\">onward</st>. Then <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">got up</st> and <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">went</st> to <st data-num=\"07414\" class=\"\">Ramah</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Now the <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">Spirit</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> had <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">turned away</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">from</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st>, and an <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st> <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">spirit</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">from</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01204\" class=\"\">tormented</st> him.",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "Then <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servants</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> him, \u201c<st data-num=\"02009 04994\">Look</st>, an <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st> <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">spirit</st> from <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> is <st data-num=\"01204\" class=\"\">tormenting</st> you.",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"04994\" class=\"\">Let</st> our <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">lord</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">instruct</st> his <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servants</st> who are here <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> you to <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">look for</st> a <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> who <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">knows how</st> to <st data-num=\"05059\" class=\"\">play</st> the <st data-num=\"03658\" class=\"\">lyre</st>. Then <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">whenever</st> the <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st> <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">spirit</st> from <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">comes</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">upon</st> you, he can <st data-num=\"05059\" class=\"\">play</st> the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">lyre</st><n id=\"1\" /> and you will feel <st data-num=\"02895\" class=\"\">better</st>.\u201d<n id=\"2\" />",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> his <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servants</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07200 04994\">Find</st><n id=\"1\" /> me a <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> who <st data-num=\"05059\" class=\"\">plays</st> <st data-num=\"03190\" class=\"\">well</st> and <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> him <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me.\u201d ",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">One</st> of his <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">attendants</st> <st data-num=\"06030 0559\">replied</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201cI have <st data-num=\"02009 07200\">seen</st> a <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st> in <st data-num=\"01022\" class=\"\">Bethlehem</st><n id=\"2\" /> who <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">knows how</st> to <st data-num=\"05059\" class=\"\">play</st> the lyre. He is a <st data-num=\"01368 02428 \">brave</st> <st data-num=\"0376 04421\">warrior</st><n id=\"3\" /> and is <st data-num=\"0995 01697\">articulate</st><n id=\"4\" /> and <st data-num=\"0376 08389\">handsome</st>,<n id=\"5\" /> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> him.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">messengers</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07971 0413\">Send</st> me your <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>, <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> is out with the <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">sheep</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st> <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">took</st> a <st data-num=\"02543\" class=\"\">donkey</st> loaded with <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">bread</st>, a <st data-num=\"04997\" class=\"\">container</st> of <st data-num=\"03196\" class=\"\">wine</st>, and <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">a</st> <st data-num=\"01423\" class=\"\">young</st> <st data-num=\"05795\" class=\"\">goat</st><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> them <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">with</st><n id=\"2\" /> his <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>. ",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> and <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">stood</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> him. Saul <st data-num=\"0157\" class=\"\">liked</st> him a <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">great deal</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> and he <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">became</st> his <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">armor</st>-<st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">bearer</st>. ",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "Then <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> word <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03448\" class=\"\">Jesse</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04994\" class=\"\">Let</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">be</st> my <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">servant</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"04672 02580\">am very pleased with</st> him.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">whenever</st> the <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">spirit</st> from <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> would <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">upon</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st>, <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> would <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">take</st> his <st data-num=\"03658\" class=\"\">lyre</st> and <st data-num=\"05059\" class=\"\">play</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">it</st>. This would bring <st data-num=\"07304\" class=\"\">relief</st> to <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> and make him feel <st data-num=\"02895\" class=\"\">better</st>. Then the <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st> <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">spirit</st> would <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">leave</st> him <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">alone</st>.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "23"
  }
]